  "title": "人类程序员依然远强于 LLM：为什么说 AI 目前还差点火候",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==&mid=2247504901&idx=1&sn=1290aab579468277bc501dad134c3dc9&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-06-02 11:53:00",
